---
layout: base.njk
tags: projects
order: 3
title: Doodles
---

<article class="projects doodles-gallery">
  <div class="header">
    <div>
      <h1>Doodles</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="lead">
    Tiny single-file web toys reminiscent of the flash games of old. Each one is
    self-contained, with no build step and no dependencies beyond a CDN, spun up from a prompt
    or two. Click in and play; the prompts that made each one are right there on the page.
  </p>

  <div class="cards">
    {% set doodles = collections.doodles | reverse %}
    {%- for doodle in doodles -%}
      <div class="card">
        <div>
          <h3>
            <a href="{{ doodle.url }}">{{ doodle.data.title }}</a>
          </h3>
          <p class="muted">{{ doodle.data.description | safe }}</p>
          <p class="doodle-tags muted">
            {{ doodle.data.tool }}{% if doodle.data.model %} · {{ doodle.data.model }}{% endif %}
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="{{ doodle.data.image }}" alt="{{ doodle.data.title }}"/>
        </div>
      </div>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</article>
